"hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">content</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag">=</span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-string">”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"> </span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-attr">utf-8</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag">″ /&gt;</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>  </code></pre></div><div><span><span></span></span><p>为提高字符集，建议采用“utf-8”。<br><br><br></p><p>3. 调用样式表：<br><br>外部样式表调用：<br><br>页面内嵌法：就是将样式表直接写在页面代码的head区。 如：</p><div><div><br></div><div>XML/HTML代码</div></div><div><pre><code class="html hljs xml"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-tag"><span class="hljs-